<section>
<title>2.0 – Mìmís</title>

<section>
<title>Structure</title>

<a href="app/">
  <message>
    <img role="icon" src=".../co/Google/logo/button/" alt="Google"/>
    <p>Current development is on an <a href="http://code.google.com/appengine/">App Engine</a> application.</p>
  </message>
</a>

<p>The app engine application will try to maintain the largest up to date hash tree representing the state of the exterior network.</p>

<p>The cluster application is simulating the network and trying to optimally release updates to the graph.</p>

<p>It also provides the level of storage necessary to calulate the desired value for a string, meaning, how much do the people who produced that string think should be paid to consume it.</p>

</section>

